        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35287021/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35287021/" class="">第78页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ouyio1/" class=" " title="▲">▲</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="35287021">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">功利主义者批判密尔的背叛，功利主义批判者不满他对功利主义原则的忠贞。自由主义者批判他在经济学理论中向社会主义暗送秋波，社会主义者则不满他在几乎所有问题上为自由主义辩护，保守主义不满他学说中体现的对个人权利近乎无条件的强调。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-06-03 16:02</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>功利主义者批判密尔的背叛，功利主义批判者不满他对功利主义原则的忠贞。自由主义者批判他在经济学理论中向社会主义暗送秋波，社会主义者则不满他在几乎所有问题上为自由主义辩护，保守主义不满他学说中体现的对个人权利近乎无条件的强调。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35287021/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2015-06-03 16:02
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  

    </div>
      <div class="ft">
        <p class="trr">&gt; <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/2974917/annotation">更多读书笔记（共26篇）</a></p>
